<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">核心功能</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">为您的软件提供<br><span class="gradient-text">全方位保护</span></h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        密友采用先进的加密技术，直接修改程序二进制文件，不依赖后台进程，<br>
        确保您的软件安全可靠，防止未授权使用和非法传播。
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>密码保护任何程序</h3>
        <p>支持所有 32/64 位 Windows 可执行文件。无论是聊天软件、多媒体播放器还是游戏，都可以轻松加密保护。</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>支持 .exe 可执行文件</li>
          <li>兼容 Windows 7/8/10/11</li>
          <li>不影响程序正常运行</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card highlight">
        <div class="card-badge">核心优势</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>硬件绑定授权</h3>
        <p>机器码与硬件深度绑定，每台电脑生成专属密码。未授权电脑无法运行受保护的程序，有效防止软件非法传播。</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>深度硬件绑定技术</li>
          <li>一机一码专属授权</li>
          <li>防止未授权使用</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card highlight">
        <div class="card-badge">核心优势</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"></path><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>系统更新无忧</h3>
        <p>不受 Windows 系统更新影响，一次加密永久有效。即使重装系统，已授权的程序仍可正常使用。</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>不受系统更新影响</li>
          <li>重装系统后依然有效</li>
          <li>一次加密永久保护</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>安全可靠</h3>
        <p>直接修改程序二进制文件本身，不依赖后台进程运行。无法通过结束进程或删除启动项来破解保护。</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>修改二进制文件</li>
          <li>不依赖后台进程</li>
          <li>无法被简单破解</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>简单易用</h3>
        <p>三步完成加密，无需专业知识。可视化操作界面，拖拽选择程序，输入密码即可完成加密。</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>三步完成加密</li>
          <li>可视化操作界面</li>
          <li>无需专业知识</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>灵活授权</h3>
        <p>支持单机授权、批量授权，还可以设置试用期限。满足不同场景下的软件授权需求。</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>支持单机授权</li>
          <li>支持批量授权</li>
          <li>可设置试用期限</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0f 0%, #0f0f1a 100%);
    position: relative;
  }

  .features::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3), transparent);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #a5b4fc;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7, #ec4899);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 0 60px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-card.highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.05));
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
  }

  .feature-card.highlight:hover {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 0 80px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
  }

  .card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
    color: white;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2));
    border-radius: 16px;
    color: #a5b4fc;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .card-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3));
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .feature-card > p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #64748b;
    padding: 6px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #6366f1;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
